549040670.text: "As shown in Figure XREF_FIG, oral intake of apigenin at doses of 20 and 50 mug resulted in marked reduction in the protein expression of IKKalpha and its phosphorylation, NF-kB and p65 whereas a modest decrease in p-IKKbeta in PC-3 and 22Rv1 tumor xenografts."
